00:00:15.970 --> 00:00:18.930
Director of the New York
State Psychiatric Institute,

00:00:18.930 --> 00:00:21.790
and Psychiatrist in Chief
of New York Presbyterian

00:00:21.790 --> 00:00:25.940
Hospital at the Columbia
University Medical Center.

00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:28.680
Formally the President of
the American Psychiatric

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:31.170
Association, in
